author: The Current
description:
Minneapolis-based, Fargo-raised musician Walker Rider’s new alt-country LP “Fair” incorporates busy instrumentation and lo-fi production while exploring relationship complexities. 

Standout tracks like “The Comeback” were brought to life by producers Colin Miller (MJ Lenderman, Merce Lemon), Landon George (Indigo De Souza), and fellow Minnesotan Nat Harvie. Hear it Sunday nights on The Local Show. Hit Play!
title: @walkerrider444 talks about his song "The Comeback" #altcountrymusic #songwriting #shorts
